# Tailwind / shadcn bridge (consumer hybrid path)

Use with **Path B** in [consumer-bootstrap.md](../docs/consumer-bootstrap.md) §6. Path A (Shield-only) defers to [studio-dark-ui.mdc](./studio-dark-ui.mdc) and [studio-dark-shield.md](../skills/studio-dark-shield.md). Token SSoT: [TRUTH.md](../docs/TRUTH.md) §4 · [design-system-rules.mdc](./design-system-rules.mdc).

## Token bridge (Shield is SSoT)

Map tokens from `ui/msc-shield.css` into the consumer `tailwind.config.ts` (or `@theme` in Tailwind v4) — never invent parallel hex values in Tailwind config.

```ts
// Example theme.extend — values must match msc-shield.css
colors: {
  msc: {
    main: "var(--msc-bg-main)",
    surface: "var(--msc-bg-surface)",
    "surface-hover": "var(--msc-bg-surface-hover)",
    accent: "var(--msc-accent)",
    "accent-hover": "var(--msc-accent-hover)",
    "text-primary": "var(--msc-text-primary)",
    "text-secondary": "var(--msc-text-secondary)",
    border: "var(--msc-border-color)",
  },
},
borderRadius: {
  msc: "var(--msc-radius)",
},
spacing: {
  "msc-sm": "var(--msc-gap-sm)",
  "msc-md": "var(--msc-gap-md)",
  "msc-lg": "var(--msc-gap-lg)",
},
```

Load Shield CSS before Tailwind utilities so `var(--msc-*)` resolves inside `.msc-viewport-shield` / `.msc-dashboard-container`.

## Forbidden patterns

- **No** global `@apply` on `body`, `html`, or unprefixed layout tags.
- **No** hardcoded hex/rgb in TSX `style` or arbitrary Tailwind literals (`bg-[#121212]`) when a `--msc-*` token exists.
- **No** inline layout/color styles in components — use satellite CSS (`ui/msc-[feature].css`) or shadcn `className` utilities.

## shadcn / MCP discipline

- Prefer **shadcn registry** components (`npx shadcn add`, or **shadcn MCP**) for app-shell UI (forms, dialogs, tables).
- Custom Studio Dark chrome stays in **satellite files** scoped to `.msc-*` wrappers; do not fork shadcn primitives into global CSS.
- For up-to-date Tailwind/React/Next APIs, prompt with **context7** (e.g. “use context7 for Next.js 15 routing”).

## Coexistence

| Surface | Styling system |
|---------|----------------|
| Payload admin, dashboards, WordPress | Shield → Layout → Components → Feature satellites |
| Marketing / app routes (Next + shadcn) | Tailwind + shadcn + bridged `--msc-*` theme |
| Shared tokens | Always defined first in `ui/msc-shield.css` |
